This strategy enhances the traditional Supertrend by combining ATR-based volatility bands with dual moving average confirmation to improve trade selection and reduce false entries.

Core Components:

• ATR Period & Factor – Generates dynamic Supertrend bands based on market volatility.
• ALMA (Arnaud Legoux Moving Average) – Provides low-lag trend smoothing for directional bias.
• WVMA (Weighted Volume Moving Average) – Incorporates volume-weighted confirmation to filter weak or low-conviction moves.

Strategy Logic

Long positions are taken when:

Price aligns with bullish Supertrend direction

ALMA confirms upward trend structure

WVMA supports momentum through volume-weighted bias

This is a long only strategy

Objective

The strategy aims to:

Reduce whipsaws during consolidation

Improve trend confirmation in volatile markets

Increase trade quality through multi-factor validation

Fully customizable parameters (Parameters changed inside PineScript not input, only ATR and Factors can be changed within settings, the rest inside the PineScript tab.

This is a systematic, rule-based approach intended for traders who want structured trend participation rather than discretionary entries.
